"body></html>"
msgstr ""

#: /home/hu-hub/个人项目/开源项目/MouseTiler/src/contents/ui/config_strings.cpp:20
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:700; color:#ffaa00;\">READ "
"ME</span> There are a lot of settings, bust most people probably only want "
"to change 3 of them (visibility, position, and disable the hints). I have "
"marked them with <span style=\" font-weight:700; color:#ffaa00;\">IMPORTANT</"
"span> tag so they are easy to find.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""

#: /home/hu-hub/个人项目/开源项目/MouseTiler/src/contents/ui/config_strings.cpp:21
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:700;\">All Popup Grid "
